{"tid":2267737,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「光復印度」印度已封禁中共「PUBG手機版」！","createTime":"2020-11-02T09:41:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T10:06:03.000Z","uid":184099,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8bfae83149ae9b9c592d5f8ff1c7a5c3d3d7f083","tid":2267737,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:41:56.000Z","msg":"Qooah: 印度已經完全停運《PUBG Mobile》，拜拜～.<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2020/11/01/india-pubg-mobile-closed/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2020%2F11%2F01%2Findia-pubg-mobile-closed%2F&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxdKNpY%2BoLPIqDl3on0Jjdx4%3D&h=57319a10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2020/11/01/india-pubg-mobile-closed/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n示， PUBG Mobile 全球發布不久後得到了廣大玩家的喜愛，成為全球最受歡迎的手機遊戲，並且成為了印度月活（ MUA ）最高的手機遊戲，高達活躍玩家約3300萬人，但是《 PUBG Mobile 》和《 PUBG Mobile Lite 》手機遊戲運營公司已宣布 10月30日停止對印度地區的的服務。<br />\n<br />\n印度電子和信息技術部以「損害印度主權和領土完整，威脅印度國防、國家安全和公共秩序」為由，封禁了由中國公司所研發的一百多款手機app ，其中就包含了《 PUBG Mobile 》和《 PUBG Mobile Lite 》。據去年數據顯示《 PUBG Mobile 》在印度地區的平均月收入就達700萬~800萬美元，「PUBG」這款遊戲除了為遊戲運營公司帶來了收益以外，還為印度通過這款遊戲謀生的職業玩家帶來了不錯的收入，部分職業玩家就可以靠打遊戲輕鬆賺到十萬盧比。「PUBG」不再對印度營運後，對於這部分人的打擊也是十分巨大的。<br />\n<br />\n此前，印度方面還對中國的其他遊戲應用進行封禁，智明星通的《列王的紛爭》和沐瞳科技的《無盡對決》也在封禁名單上。"},{"pid":"82a06fde21871ad60e5b71d25ea506167187bcd4","tid":2267737,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:42:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1260d6c753955d2ddc232d374f39a9e0e7f1cd9f","tid":2267737,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:42:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\